let $csv-uneven-cols := concat(`date,name,city,amount,currency,original amount,note{$crlf}`, `2023-07-19,Bob,Berlin,10.00,USD,13.99{$crlf}`, `2023-07-20,Alice,Aachen,15.00{$crlf}`, `2023-07-20,Charlie,Celle,15.00,GBP,11.99,cake,not a lie{$crlf}`) return
csv-to-xml($csv-uneven-cols, map { "column-names": true(), "number-of-columns": 6 })
